Google, right? So it's not somebody--some
small random company you've never heard of,

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:33.770
so it's easy to say, "Oh, if there's a problem
I can go to Google. I can deal with that.

00:12:33.770 --> 00:12:41.279
They're going to take care of me." And because
it's part of this Web Store, it's not too

